            "id": 5938793,
            "title": "滙豐控股(005)昨在港斥2496萬元回購32.28萬股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社15日專訊》滙豐控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00005:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00005\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00005-HK</a>)公布,昨日在香港聯交所回購32.28萬股,每股價格介乎77.1元至77.45元,每股加權平均價約77.3278元,涉資約2496.14萬元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　與此同時,滙控於英國回購16.7623萬股,每股介乎7.597至7.61<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/gbpusd\">英鎊</a>,加權平均價為7.6082<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/gbpusd\">英鎊</a>,涉資127.53萬<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/gbpusd\">英鎊</a>。自2月20日開始回購以來,滙控已回購合共約1.67億股普通股,總代價約18.64億美元。(eh)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
